high_descs: Walk around the left side of the table to the couch.
Pick up the red credit card on the couch.
Turn around and walk right around the table to the other side.
Place the credit card on the table in front of the statue.
Turn left and veer left to the round table in the corner.
Pick up the red credit card on the table.
Walk ahead and left back to the coffee table.
Place the credit card on the table to the left of the first card.
anns.task_desc: Place two credit cards on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the chair, then turn right and walk around the coffee table to the couch.
Pick up the red credit card off of the seat of the couch.
Turn left and walk towards the chair, then hang a left and walk towards the door, turn left again and walk up to the side of the coffee table.
Put the red credit card on the coffee table behind the golden statue.
Turn left and walk over to the chair, then turn left and walk up to the wall, turn right and walk over to the small black table.
Pick up the red credit card off of the small black table.
Turn left and walk back over to the coffee table.
Put the red credit card onto the coffee table to the left of the credit card that is already there.
anns.task_desc: Move two credit cards to the coffee table.

high_descs: maneuver around the coffee table by making a left, then face the large couch behind the coffee table
pick up the credit card on the large couch
return to the front of the coffee table
place the credit card on the coffee table in front of the gold statue
turn around, then turn left to face the side table to the left of the couch
pick up the credit card on the side table in front of the lamp
return to the coffee table
place the credit card to the left of the first credit card on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Pick up two credit cards from around the room and place them on the coffee table
